    detail: 'Contractor website buried license info in footer. Added prominent section: "Licensed | Bonded | Insured | License #123456" with trust badges. Bid acceptance rate: 23% â†’ 38%. Homeowners are suspicious of contractors. Licensing visible = legitimate = trustworthy. One headline change = 65% more revenue from same leads. Don\'t make homeowners hunt for credibility. Put it front and center. They\'re looking for reasons NOT to hire you. Don\'t give them reasons.'
