    finding: 'Contractor with detailed project photos: 427% more quote requests',
    detail: 'Before: generic gallery of finished rooms. After: detailed project storiesâ€”"Day 1: Demolition," "Day 7: Framing complete," "Day 14: Cabinets installed," "Day 21: Finished kitchen." Each with photos, brief description. Visitors saw process, expertise, problem-solving. Quote requests: 17/month â†’ 90/month. Process photos = expertise proof. Homeowners don\'t want outcomesâ€”they want to know you can handle problems. Show your work. All of it. The messy parts too. That\'s when they trust you.'
