            <p class="text-amber-300 font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">My Experience Testing Contractor Websites</p>
            <p class="text-white/90 text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">I spent 50 hours building contractor websites on Squarespace, Wix, and Framer. I loaded real before/after photos, created project galleries, added licensing displays, built service area maps, tested quote forms. I tracked bid requests from each platform. Here's what actually happened.</p>
