        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-300 p-6 hover:border-amber-500 transition-colors">
          <p class="text-amber-600 font-black text-3xl mb-3">5</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">No Timeline = Endless Questions</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Every call: "How long will this take?" Transparent timelines ("Kitchen: 6-8 weeks") reduced "how long" questions 73%. Closing time dropped from 4 weeks to 2 weeks. Timeline transparency = professional = faster deals. The biggest homeowner complaint isn't priceâ€”it's timeline surprises. Eliminate the surprise upfront. Set expectations, deliver on them.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-300 p-6 hover:border-amber-500 transition-colors">
          <p class="text-amber-600 font-black text-3xl mb-3">6</p>
