          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm"><strong>71% of contractor traffic is mobile</strong>. Homeowners see your ad at work, click website on phone. Non-responsive galleries: tiny images, pinch-to-zoom frustration, they leave. Mobile-optimized full-width swipe: they stay, they explore, they request quote. Mobile = discovery. Desktop = detailed quote forms. Both must work or you lose the funnel to contractors with better mobile sites.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

